data.value:
Industrial Park is made by igorseabra4 using C# and SharpDX.
It is a HIP/HOP archive viewer and editor for the following games: - SpongeBob SquarePants: Battle For Bikini Bottom - The SpongeBob SquarePants Movie - Scooby-Doo: Night of 100 Frights - The Incredibles - The Incredibles: Rise of the Underminer by Heavy Iron Studios for GameCube, Xbox, PlayStation 2, PC.
Additional credits go to: - actualchatterteeth - Dark - MinecraftFreak73 - Pepperpot - Seil - Suprnova123 - TetraxZ and other members of the games' online communities for contributions on findings and code
External tools used: - TxdGen - vgmstream
For questions, suggestions, problems or any other reasons you can contact me at Heavy Iron Modding, GitHub, YouTube, or even better, on Discord: please join the Heavy Iron Modding server. ~igorseabra4
